	<br /><br />
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12" style="padding: 0px">
			<p><span style="font-weight:bold">Project Map</span><br />

			Please click on an orange cone in the project map to view more information about a TIA project.</p>
			<iframe class="frame-map" src="http://gis10.dot.ga.gov/FeaturedProjects/map.html"></iframe>
		</div>
	</div>